attributes.Long form description: The student starts by assembling the legs and screwing them with a screw. After that, the student assembles the curved legs doing the same process. The student continues to assemble the curved legs with the straight legs and secrews them with screws. When the student finishes doing that, he proceeds to assemble the grid trays to the frame, using screws to do it.  Finally, the student assembles the wheels.
